Name: infrastructure-diagrams
Version: 0.0.4
Summary: Create infrastructure diagrams from configuration files (YAML and JSON) by using Graphviz
Home-page: https://github.com/kotlarz/infrastructure-diagrams
Author: Marius Kotlarz
Author-email: marius.kotlarz@gmail.com
